extends ../layouts/default
append headExt
  link(rel="stylesheet" href="/css/views/reset_pwd.css")
block content
  if(success === '1')
    h3.resetPassword.text-center 我们已经向您的邮箱发送了链接请登陆您的邮箱进行验证
  else
    form.resetPassword.form-horizontal(action="/company/forgetPassword" method="post")
        h1.text-center 请输入要找回密码的账号
        hr
        .form-group
          .col-md-4.col-md-offset-4
            input.form-control.dl_reset(type="email" name="email" placeholder="请输入验证邮箱" required)
        if err
          .form-group
            .col-md-4.col-md-offset-4
              label.dl_err.dl_reset= err
        .form-group
          .col-md-offset-5.col-md-2
            button.dl_reset.btn-block.btn.btn-primary(type="submit") 下一步